  "text": "In the following experiments, all the CT images containing lobulation sign come from our LISS database [CITATION_1] , which can be downloaded from the website: http:// www.iscbit.org/LISS.html. LISS database is a publicly available database of Lung CT Imaging Signs, and it contains 271 CT scans, in which 677 abnormal regions corresponding to 9 categories of common CT imaging signs of lung diseases (CISLs) are detected and labeled by radiologists. Figure 9 shows some examples. For lobulation signs, LISS database contains 41 lobulation samples.",
